==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ὄνομα / onoma / on'-om-ah

===Etymology===
*From a presumed derivative of the base of [[γινώσκω]] (compare [[ὀνίνημι]]); a “name” (literally or figuratively), (authority, character): 

===Noun===
'''ὄνομα'''

# called, (+ sur-) [[name]] (-d).

